comments: Mitchell's (CLE) off-arm comes out slightly as he spins away from Martin (MIA) and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Martin (MIA) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Butler (MIA)is the last player to touch the ball prior to going out of bounds.  Possession is awarded to Cleveland.
Herro (MIA) and Okoro (CLE) engage and disengage as the screen is set and the contact is marginal.
Okoro (CLE) gathers the ball and steps his left foot out of bounds. Possession is properly conferred to Miami.
Vincent (MIA) establishes himself in Mobley's (CLE) path and does not deliver contact while setting the pick.
Mobley (CLE) legally contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) is unable to inbound the ball within five seconds after receiving it from the official.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his collapsed forearm to Allen's (CLE) side and marginal contact occurs as Adebayo deflects the inbound pass.
Herro (MIA) places and removes his hands from LeVert's (CLE) side as he goes to set the pick and the contact is marginal.
Butler (MIA) legally contests Mobley's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Vincent (MIA) establishes himself in Mobley's (CLE) path and absorbs the contact.
Garland (CLE) jumps alongside Butler's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Allen (CLE) and Adebayo (MIA) mutually engage and disengage during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Garland (CLE) legally contests Vincent's (MIA) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) steps into Mobley's (CLE) space and initiates body contact that affects his shot attempt near the basket.
Mitchell (CLE) lightly brushes Herro's (MIA) right arm while he is in possession of the ball. The contact on the play is marginal.
Garland (CLE) aligns along Vincent's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs at the beginning of Vincent's dribble.
Mobley (CLE) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) and Allen (CLE) jostle for position during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Mitchell (CLE) commits a take foul on Adebayo (MIA).
Butler (MIA) and LeVert (CLE) engage during the inbound play and marginal contact occurs as Butler releases away from the defender.
LeVert (CLE) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Mobley (CLE) briefly places and removes his hand from Adebayo's (MIA) arm during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Vincent (MIA) places and promptly removes his hand from Garland's (CLE) front prior to the screen and the contact is marginal.
Vincent (MIA) legally contests Garland's (CLE) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Okoro (CLE) slides his arm off of Herro (MIA) and the contact during the inbound is marginal.
Okoro (CLE) and Martin (MIA) break in separate directions and incidental foot to foot contact occurs during the inbound.
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Butler (MIA) lightly brushes Mitchell's (CLE) side prior to gathering the ball and beginning his upward shooting motion.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) perimeter jump shot attempt. Mitchell proceeds to go to the ground on his own accord.
